n skulle kanskje se ny ut til jul, bryllup eller sommerferie. N\u00e5 er det tykt av mannfolk her hver eneste l\u00f8rdag.", "Fin p\u00e5 h\u00e5ret hele \u00e5ret: \u00abJaja, enten er man heldig p\u00e5 bilder, eller s\u00e5 er man bare lik seg selv\u00bb, sier Ruth Irene Fossum som torsdag kan feire 40-\u00e5rsjubileum for sin fris\u00f8rsalong p\u00e5 By\u00e5sen."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|trondheim"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "cc9be067ad59bc14d3b7ca3fe127e2ff9880d6a893668b901d66fdea1a2bb873"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2016-12-30T08:11:41.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "OVERTRO: Hennes f\u00f8rste dag som gift var den syvende, hun \u00e5pnet fris\u00f8rsalongen den syvende og skulle gjerne f\u00e5tt alle sine barn p\u00e5 den syvende."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1053995.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/ver2%20Klarinettfrisoer.jpg-000"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/5625cb934bda3a606ad1c455ff3f27493310c13d.jpg?59726bd3"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "Velstelt h\u00e5r i 40 \u00e5r -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "5625cb934bda3a606ad1c455ff3f27493310c13d"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "trondheim"]}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["velstelt", "salong", "h\u00e5r", "velstelt h\u00e5r", "fris\u00f8rsalong"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["livets", "klippotequet", "norges", "klarinett salong", "trondheim symfoniorkester", "by\u00e5sen", "hallset", "charisma"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["bod\